--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Setting an Environment Variable
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    $ export VAR_NAME=VALUE


e.g.: Setting the cvs root directory:

    $ export CVSROOT=/usr/local/bin/cvs


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
See the value of a variable
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    $ echo $VAR_NAME

e.g.: Checking the value of CVSROOT

    $ echo $CVSROOT


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Unsetting a Variable
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    $ unset VAR_NAME


e.g.: Unsetting the CVSROOT var:

    $ unset CVSROOT
